reference: Reinhold Remmert, Classical topics in complex function theory, Vol. 172 of Graduate Texts in Mathematics, p. 12, Springer, 1997.
formula: Binomial(2, 1+i) = 1/(i!*(-i)!) (where x! means Gamma(x+1)). - _Robert G. Wilson v_, Feb 23 2015
